high_descs: Pick up the white object from the sink.
Open the fridge, place the object inside and close it.
Reclaim the object, walk over to the trash.
Throw the object in the trash.
anns.task_desc: Throw the white object from the sink into the trash.

high_descs: Turn around, then make a left to go to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the orange next to the sponge.
Go to the fridge on the wall opposite the sink.
Open the fridge and place the orange with the other oranges, close the door, and then open it again to take out the orange you just put inside.
Turn to the left until you reach the wall, then go straight to the waste bin.
Throw the orange in the waste bin.
anns.task_desc: Removing an orange from the sink for cooling and throwing away.

high_descs: Go to the sink behind you and to your left.
Pick up the egg that is next to the sponge.
Go to the fridge behind you.
Chill the egg in the fridge.
Go to the trash bin behind you and in the corner.
Place the egg in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold egg in the trash.
